    <item>
      <title>英国与沙特阿拉伯在利雅得举行联合峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-14/uk-saudi-arabia-hold-joint-summit-in-riyadh-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯和英国今天在利雅得举行联合峰会，两国都希望加强经济联系并促进投资。出席会议的 450 多名英国代表中包括汇丰银行 (HSBC) 和英国航空公司 (British Airways) 的高管。彭博新闻社的克里斯蒂娜·伯克 (Christine Burke) 与 Joumanna Bercetche 讨论中东和非洲地平线。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-14/uk-saudi-arabia-hold-joint-summit-in-riyadh-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:52:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通胀担忧缓解，挪威加大石油财富支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/norway-dials-up-spending-of-oil-wealth-as-inflation-worry-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威计划将其 1.6 万亿美元主权财富基金的支出超出先前计划，以帮助北欧国家克服降息预期延迟带来的经济疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/norway-dials-up-spending-of-oil-wealth-as-inflation-worry-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:41:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>非洲的可持续发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-14/sustainable-development-in-africa</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国助理秘书长兼开发计划署非洲区域主任阿洪娜·埃齐亚孔瓦表示，由于陷入僵局，非洲不太可能实现 2030 年可持续发展目标，但通过利用基础设施投资和社会支出项目还是有希望的。她与 Jennifer Zabasajja 和 Joumanna Bercetche 就《中东和非洲地平线》进行了独家对话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-14/sustainable-development-in-africa</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:25:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团退出钻石和铂金业务以抵御必和必拓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/anglo-to-exit-diamonds-and-platinum-in-bid-to-fend-off-bhp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 将退出钻石、铂金和煤炭开采业，进行大规模重组，旨在抵御竞争对手必和必拓 (BHP) 集团的收购，并将这家拥有 107 年历史的矿业公司转变为铜业巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/anglo-to-exit-diamonds-and-platinum-in-bid-to-fend-off-bhp</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国就业市场持续降温，英国央行继续裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/uk-unemployment-rate-rises-to-highest-since-last-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国失业率上升，私营部门工资增长放缓，这些迹象表明劳动力市场普遍降温，这可能会让英国央行更有信心在未来几个月降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/uk-unemployment-rate-rises-to-highest-since-last-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 06:09:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
